System:

    melt of 100 chains of 8 atoms.

    Requires a version of ddSim compiled with angles (-a)
    and dihedrals (-d) enabled.

Usage:

Parallel NVE md simulation on 4 processors:

    mpirun -np 4 ddSim -e -p param -c commands

Restarting and extending previous simulation

    mpirun -np 4 ddSim -e -r restart -c commands.rst
